25/05/2003
ZAGREB, Croatia -- The Croatian capital will host the 25th Jubilee Conference of Chiefs of police of the European capitals, according to the Zagreb police on Saturday (24 May).The forum will take place from 26 May to 30 May.Croatian Prime Minister Ivica Racan and Interior Minister Sime Lucin will open the sessions. 
According to the Zagreb police, 36 European police chiefs have confirmed participation so far. 
(HINA - 24/05/03)
